Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:37.48,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}究竟有多少是真心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:43.32,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}谁也不能给我答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:47.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)\pos(840,710)}珍贵没有唯一定义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:51.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)\pos(840,710)}论多么渺小的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:59.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)\pos(840,710)}也能找到特殊的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:03.22,EDCN3,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}无论你拥有何种外表
